OL,3,CPlaid Cymru pledge new payments for
OL,4,Cfamilies to tackle child poverty
OL,6,FPlaid Cymru's leader has promised to
OL,7,Fintroduce a child payment to the
OL,8,Fhardest-hit families here in Wales if
OL,9,Fhe becomes First Minister after next
OL,10,Fyear's Senedd election.
OL,12,FRhun ap Iorwerth announced the policy
OL,13,Ffor the 'Cynal' payment at his party's
OL,14,Fconference in Llandudno on Friday.
OL,16,FHe told members that a Plaid Cymru
OL,17,FWelsh Government would seek to carry
OL,18,Fout a pilot, expected to cost #10m a
OL,19,Fyear, that would see those families
OL,20,Fwho claim Universal Credit receive an
OL,21,Fextra #10 a week per child.
