OL,6,FIt is estimated that this pilot could
OL,7,Fbenefit 15,000 households initially.
OL,9,FSpeaking at the spring conference,
OL,10,FRhun ap Iorwerth said his party would
OL,11,F"draw on the experience in Scotland"
OL,12,Fand "begin the process of implementing
OL,13,Fa child payment in Wales ` a weekly
OL,14,Fdirect benefit to support those who
OL,15,Fneed it the most".
OL,17,FHowever, the current Labour First
OL,18,FMinister Eluned Morgan said that the
OL,19,Fconference speech was "full of hot
OL,20,Fair".
