OL,6,FShe said people should not forget
OL,7,FPlaid MSs "all voted against #26
OL,8,Fbillion for Wales" when they voted
OL,9,Fagainst the recent Welsh budget.
OL,11,FShe added: "Words, words, words, but
OL,12,Fwhen it comes to action, he turns his
OL,13,Fback on the people of Wales."
OL,15,FDuring his conference speech, Rhun Ap
OL,16,FIorwerth said that child poverty is a
OL,17,F"national stain" on Wales which leaves
OL,18,F"an indelible mark on communities the
OL,19,Flength and breadth of our country".
